quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,Alif lam Mim
  2,2,Esho nishio eshitabu shibulamwo obukanakani nishiobulunjifu khubalia abaria Nyasaye
  2,3,"Balia abasuubilanga mubilalolekha, abaswaliyanga (iswala) khatsotso, ne barusinjia eshihanwa khumukabo kwa khubakabile"
  2,4,"Balia basuubilanga khu kalia keshibwa khwiwe, nende kalia keshibwa imbeli wuwo, ne basuubilanga muno inyanga yeyindukho"
  2,5,"Abo bali khubulunjifu okhurula khu Nyasaye wabu, ne abo nibobalibura"
  2,6,"Toto balia abakhaya ni halalasa awo, obekanyilisie nohomba oleshe okhubekanyilisia shibalisuubila tawe"
  2,7,"Nyasaye yara eshifunikho khumioyo chiabu nende khutsimbulililo tsiabu nende khutsindolelo tsiabu, mana bali nende eshinyasio eshilulu"